  "title": "Secretary cum HR Executive (Financial Services)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Provide comprehensive secretarial and administrative support to senior management, managing schedules, priorities, and daily executive operations with a high level of discretion.</li><li>Serve as the primary contact for the executive office, coordinating with board members, investors, senior management, and external stakeholders.</li><li>Prepare and manage executive communications, presentations, and materials, as well as organize board meetings and corporate engagements.</li><li>Support talent acquisition and HR-related initiatives, including sourcing, recruiter coordination, onboarding, and special confidential projects.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Diploma or Degree in Business Administration, Human Resources, or equivalent.</li><li>At least 5 years of experience in <strong>executive support, office management, or HR administration, preferably supporting senior leadership.</strong></li><li>Hands-on exposure to recruitment processes and familiarity with Singapore employment practices.</li><li>Highly organized, professional, and independent, with strong communication skills and the ability to operate in a fast-paced environment.</li></ul><p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p><p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p><p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p><p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
